# SpotGov Design System

**Source of truth:** [`AGENTS.md`](../../AGENTS.md) — read it before building or editing UI.

**Fast inventory:** [`docs/component-manifest.md`](../../docs/component-manifest.md) (`npm run generate:manifest` after adding components).

**Which-one-when:** [`docs/design-system.md`](../../docs/design-system.md) §8 · [`docs/component-patterns.md`](../../docs/component-patterns.md)

## Non-negotiables (summary)

- Semantic tokens only — `bg-bg-*`, `text-text-*`, `primary-base`; no raw hex
- Import primitives from `@/components/ui/*`; prefer **canonical blocks** from the manifest
- `@remixicon/react` Line icons; AlignUI type utilities (`text-title-h6`, `text-label-*`, `text-paragraph-*`)
- Light-only product UI; WCAG 2.1 AA; status = text + icon/shape
- Copy from [`docs/copy.md`](../../docs/copy.md); no em dashes in product UI

Do not duplicate the full rulebook in this file.
